ashakiran07.github.io/Tic-Tac-Toe/

## INTRO:
Tic Tac Toe is a classic game played on a 3x3 grid where players take turns marking spaces with their symbols (usually "X" and "O") until one player wins by placing three of their symbols in a row, column, or diagonal, or the game ends in a draw.

## FEATURES:
-Play against the computer AI.
-Simple and intuitive user interface.
-Automatic detection of the winner or draw.
-Replay option to start a new game.

## How To Play
  1. Open the game in a web browser.
  2. Select whether you want to play as "X" or "O".
  3. Click on the empty cells in the grid to make your move.
  4. If playing against the computer, wait for the AI to make its move.
  5. The game will automatically detect if there's a winner or if it's a draw.
  6. Use the replay button to start a new game.

## TECHNOLOGIES USED:
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
Usage
Clone the repository or download the files.
Open index.html in a web browser.
Follow the on-screen instructions to play the game.

